                        <p>This opportunity offers special financial services to clients requiring deferred credit line enhancements, collateral backed funding or premium insurance funding. This service is purposed to provide clients with the ability to secure funds or assets to its funding entity or providers.</p>
                        <h3>Project Deferred Assets</h3>
                        <p>The project deferred asset platform provides clients with newly issued bank rated instruments such as Bank Guarantee (BG) or Standby Letter of Credit (SBLC). This allows the client to either lease or purchase the instruments at a low discount price with deferment options on the back end.</p>
                        <h3>Project Endorsed Funding</h3>
                        <p>The project endorsed funding is a great way to secure 100% funding. With this platform, the client will be able to introduce acceptable collateral backed by their financial institution. This makes funding suitable to clients presenting endorsed instruments very favorable to our lending partners.</p>
